%div{ class: "min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center py-12" }
  %div{ class: "max-w-xl w-full mx-4" }
    %div{ class: "bg-slate-900/80 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-800 p-8 space-y-6" }

      %div{ class: "space-y-2" }
        %h1{ class: "text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight" } Story Game
        %p{ class: "text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sky-400" }
          Single-player interactive story

      %div{ class: "text-slate-200 leading-relaxed space-y-2" }
        %p
          | You find yourself at the beginning of a winding tale with uncertain endings.
        %p.text-sm.text-slate-400
          | Your choices will shape what happens next.

      / Start new game form (asks for name)
      %div{ class: "mt-6 border-t border-slate-800 pt-4 space-y-4" }
        %h2{ class: "text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300" } Start a new game

        = form_with url: start_game_path, method: :post, local: true do |f|
          %div{ class: "space-y-2" }
            %label{ class: "block text-xs font-medium text-slate-400" }
              Player name
            = f.text_field :player_name,
              value: @player_name,
              placeholder: "Traveler",
              class: "w-full rounded-md bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-100 placeholder:text-slate-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:ring-sky-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-slate-950"

          %div{ class: "mt-3" }
            = f.submit "Start game",
              class: "inline-flex items-center px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-400 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 transition focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:ring-sky-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-slate-950"

      - if @can_continue
        %div{ class: "mt-6 border-t border-slate-800 pt-4 space-y-3" }
          %h2{ class: "text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300" } Continue

          %p{ class: "text-xs text-slate-400" }
            - if @player_name.present?
              = "Last played as #{@player_name}."
            - else
              | Last game in progress.

          = link_to "Continue game",
            story_node_path(session[:current_node_id]),
            class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-slate-700 hover:border-sky-400 hover:bg-slate-900/80 text-xs font-medium text-slate-100 transition focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:ring-sky-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-slate-950"
